<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="not-answered">Braille translation service <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Disabled WC <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Text Relay <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Step free access <span>(not answered)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent282abb221dde484ab9b20d5b031cd906">
</div>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-2">Accommodation</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Access to TV<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Internet access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Public telephone<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Family accommodation <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Mobile phones permitted <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Private rooms only <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="no">Single sex accommodation only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent577dfd77960046bfb49b4dac781dd323">
</div>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-4">Counselling and Support</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="not-answered">Bereavement support <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Translation services <span>(not answered)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentfdbc96abd8374831a74b36a5e77fb745">
</div>
<p>The hospital has a whole range of services that support patients and their carers in different ways. These include bereavement support, art therapists and psychological care services. The Pastoral &amp; Psychological Care Team has designated counselling rooms.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="not-answered">Prayer area <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">On-site chapel <span>(not answered)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentdede89beb59d4cdfb3837f6b665fdb14">
</div>
<p>There is a chapel at The Royal Marsden's Sutton site as well as a separate prayer room. Both are open around the clock. The hospital chaplains, who represent many different world faiths, can be contacted through the main hospital switchboard. They will be there for you if you are a patient, visitor or member of staff, and whether or not you have a religious faith.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Patient library <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Pharmacy <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent3d294ee8eec64630939c594ddeee24e9">
</div>
<p>All areas of the hospital are accessible to wheelchair users using a combination of ramps and lifts. Hearing loops are also provided in the pharmacy and outpatient department. Telephones for the use of patients with hearing aids are available in the Facilities Office.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentabb599964bcb409dbf93750a8b3c0097">
</div>
<p>Parking at the hospital is on a barrier pay-on-exit scheme. Parking is on a ‘pay on foot’ basis and charges are as follows:</p>
<ul class="bullet">
<li>Up to ½ hour: free </li>
<li>½–1 hour: £2 </li>
<li>1–2 hours: £4 </li>
<li>2–3 hours: £6 </li>
<li>3–4 hours: £8 </li>
<li>4–5 hours: £10 </li>
<li>5–8 hours: £12 </li>
<li>8–24 hours: £14 </li>
<li>Weekly (7 day) permit: £25 </li>
<li>Monthly (30 day) permit: £50 </li>
<li>6-week (45 day) permit: £60 </li>
<li>Annual permit: £100</li>
</ul>
<p>Lost tickets are charged at the daily rate.</p>
<p>Parking fees for stays up to 24 hours can be paid for at the barrier on  exiting the car park.</p>
</div>
